lead_paragraph: Third-round play at the weather-disrupted Zurich Classic of New Orleans was suspended for the day after just 75 minutes of action on Saturday, setting up the possibility of a Monday finish at the TPC Louisiana.

headline.print_headline: Monday Finish on the Cards in Weather-Hit New Orleans
